t:
Humpty Dumpty sat on a wall,
Humpty Dumpty had a great fall.

All the king's horses and all the king's men



    watched in horror as she flung
    herself to certain death jumping
    from the high rise building.
c:
Suicide is not the answer. It is the question.
The answer is not so rhyming though.
